INSERT INTO `adminnotification_inbox` VALUES (1,4,'2020-02-03 19:53:41','You are invited: Seize the New Year– 5 Growth Strategies for 2020.','Join us for a live webinar on February 13th with Magento experts Shannon Hane and Matthew Wasley from Adobe to learn the latest eCommerce strategies to accelerate revenue growth in 2020. Register today: http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b','http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b',1,0),(2,4,'2020-02-10 16:41:26','Are you putting off integrating your ERP and eCommerce?','Get started on the journey to a more integrated and profitable eCommerce business. Download our comprehensive guide, eCommerce + ERP: Better Together. http://bit.ly/33XMHVV','http://bit.ly/33XMHVV',1,0),(3,4,'2020-02-12 15:11:23','Join Tomorrow\'s Webinar: Seize the New Year– 5 Growth Strategies for 2020.','Join us for a live webinar tomorrow, February 13th with Magento experts Shannon Hane and Matthew Wasley from Adobe to learn the latest eCommerce strategies to accelerate revenue growth in 2020. Register today: http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b','http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b',0,0),(4,4,'2020-02-28 14:39:26','2020 goal: Is your product content keeping up with your customers?','Magento Page Builder gives you fast content updates and even faster growth. Download our eBook to learn more. Link here: http://bit.ly/2NyTuQf','http://bit.ly/2NyTuQf',0,0),(5,1,'2020-03-05 21:25:23','Retrieving data. Wait a few seconds and try to cut or copy again.','&quot;We have discovered an error in Magento 2.3.4 that can prevent a shopper from completing an order when using PayPal Express Checkout. The issue occurs for any country where the region field in the address section is a text field (as opposed to a drop-down menu).\nWe have released a hotfix to resolve this issue and recommend that merchants on Magento version 2.3.4 who are also using PayPal Express Checkout download and apply this hotfix as soon as possible to prevent further errors. Please refer to our help center for instructions and troubleshooting. A fix for this issue will be included in Magento 2.3.5.','https://support.magento.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039451972',0,0),(6,4,'2020-03-16 00:00:00','St. Patrick\'s Day Sale Announcement','20% discount on every extension is on NOW. Ends on March 18th, don\'t miss out','https://www.mageplaza.com/deals/?utm_source=notification&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sale-12',0,0),(7,4,'2020-03-20 15:03:20','Simplify and accelerate your content updates with Page Builder','Content is critical to eCommerce engagement. In fact, 87 percent of shoppers say product content has a high impact on their purchasing decisions. Page Builder delivers a drag-and-drop content creation and management tool which simplifies your website updates from start to finish. Learn how this powerful creative tool can grow your business. Link here: http://bit.ly/2NyTuQf','http://bit.ly/2NyTuQf',0,0),(8,1,'2020-03-24 16:02:43','Important Hot Fix Available for Magento Commerce 2.3','A new Hot Fix is available to close a security issue in Magento Open Source 2.3, all versions. We recommend that users of potentially affected deployments take immediate action by updating your Magento installation with the latest patch. Please review our Security Blog via the included link for more information about the bug and how to apply the Hot Fix.','https://magento.com/security/hot-fix-available-cve-2019-8118',0,0),(9,4,'2020-04-08 16:41:38','Watch On-Demand Webinar: Seize the New Year– 5 Growth Strategies for 2020.','Magento experts Shannon Hane and Matthew Wasley from Adobe will share the latest eCommerce strategies to accelerate revenue growth in 2020. Watch now: http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b','http://bit.ly/2GPpb4b',0,0),(10,4,'2020-04-10 17:14:30','You are invited! Join our live webinar on April 23rd: The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2.','Join us for The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2 webinar on April 23rd. John Glasgow and Matt Boland from Adobe will discuss how your business can reduce operating costs and grow revenue. Leading solution partner Atwix will also share how they are helping customers launch innovative solutions to meet expectations in today’s environment. Register Now: https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX','https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX',0,0),(11,4,'2020-04-14 22:03:09','Upgrade to Magento Commerce with no payments for the first 3 months. ','Adobe is committed to supporting merchants during this challenging time. Upgrade to Magento Commerce 2 quickly and affordably with limited time offers. Pay nothing for the first 3 months, and our Magento Commerce launch package will get you up and running fast. Free Magento U classes will ensure your teams are fully equipped to take their digital operations to the next level. Learn more: https://bit.ly/2RBnk8M','https://bit.ly/2RBnk8M',0,0),(12,4,'2020-03-25 00:00:00','COVID-19 Mageplaza Support Campaign','25% discount on all extensions for young business during the coronavirus pandemic. Check it out','https://www.mageplaza.com/blog/covid-mageplaza-support-young-ebusiness-during-pandemic.html?utm_source=notification&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sale-12',0,0),(13,4,'2020-04-22 16:52:09','Join Tomorrow\'s Webinar: The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2.','Join us for a live webinar tomorrow, April 23rd. John Glasgow and Tricia Lee from Adobe will discuss how your business can reduce operating costs and grow revenue. They will also review special limited time offers. Slava Kravchuk from Atwix, # 1 Contributing Partner, will also share a customer case study leading the way in innovative B2B retail experiences. Register Now: https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX','https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX',0,0),(14,1,'2020-04-28 18:29:06','Magento Open Source 2.3.5-p1 delivers important security updates and features ','The latest releases of Magento Open Source – 2.3.5-p1 and 2.3.4-p2 – are now generally available. The latest release of Magento Open Source includes important security enhancements along with new functionality and platform quality improvements. With these importa